## Pilaf Rice {T-15min}

[Toast] The @basmati rice{200g} in a bit of oil in a #small pot{}.

[Add] The @chicken stock{200% @basmati rice}.

[Cook] Cover and simmer until liquid is absorbed (~{12min}).
